quran[9{c,v,t}:
16,94,"( aur ae mslmano, ) tum apni qasmon ko aapas mein aik dosray ko dhoka dainay ka zareya nah bana lena, kahin aisa nah ho ke koi qadam jamnay ke baad akhar jaye aur tum iss jurm ki Padaash mein ke tum ne logon ko Allah ki raah se roka, bura nateeja dekho aur sakht saza bhgto"
16,95,"Allah ke ehad ko thoray se faiday ke badlay nah beech daalo, jo kuch Allah ke paas hai woh tumahray liye ziyada behtar hai agar tum jano"
16,96,"jo kuch tumahray paas hai woh kharch ho jaane wala hai aur jo kuch Allah ke paas hai wohi baqi rehne wala hai, aur hum zaroor sabr se kaam lainay walon ko unn ke ajar unn ke behtareen aamaal ke mutabiq den ge"
16,97,"jo shakhs bhi naik amal kere ga, khuwa woh mard ho ya aurat, basharteh kehho woh momin, usay hum duniya mein pakeeza zindagi busr karayen ge aur ( akhirat mein ) aisay logon ko un ke ajar un ke behtareen aamaal ke mutabiq bakhsheen ge"
16,98,phir jab tum quran parhnay lagu to shetan rjim se khuda ki panah maang liya karo
16,99,ussay unn logon par tasallut haasil nahi hota jo imaan laatay aur apne rab par bhrosa karte hain
16,100,is ka zor to unhi logon par chalta hai jo is ko apna sarparast banatay aur is ke behkanay se shirk karte hain
16,101,jab hum aik aayat ki jagah doosri aayat nazil karte hain aur Allah behtar jaanta hai ke woh kya nazil kere to yeh log kehte hain ke tum yeh quran khoo daal ghurr te ho asal baat yeh hai ke inn mein se aksar log haqeeqat se nawaqif hain
16,102,inn se kaho ke isay to rooh al quds ne theek theek mere rab ki taraf se batadreej nazil kya hai taakay imaan laane walon ke imaan ko pukhta kere aur farmaa bardaroon ko zindagi ke mamlaat mein seedhi raah betaye aur unhen Falah o Saadat ki khush khaberi day
